        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Bipartisan Solution to Cyclical Violence Act of 2020</b></p> <p>This bill directs the Department of Health and Human Services to establish a grant program for specified trauma centers and nonprofits to establish or expand intervention or prevention programs related to intentional violent trauma, excluding intimate partner violence. </p>]]></text>
      </summary>
